data.name: Kaznews
data.description: Kaznews is a web application based on react js technologies and backend parts on Django rest framework, using api axios. In Kaznews you can write posts if this post is approved by the site administrator, then it is published, it has its own admin panel

data.name: T-mart, e-commerce
data.description: My second project is also an online store with django 4.0, ajax with the possibility of e-mail confirmation and two admin panels, one for the superadmin and the second for the admins

data.name: Kaznews API docs
